0:06:19.802,0:06:23.971
ALOY: Can't see a way to close the vent from here, I'll have to go over.

0:06:28.300,0:06:29.787
ALOY: Better time this right.

0:06:55.034,0:06:57.839
ALOY: One of these conveyors should get me across.

