0:13:21.861,0:13:25.070
ALOY: "Hephaestus" — what kind of name is that?

0:13:25.220,0:13:28.529
OUREA: Perhaps the spirit will tell us, if there are more messages.

0:13:28.529,0:13:31.519
ALOY: Maybe you're right. Let's keep moving.

